data.description: Great opportunity to own this lovely home that overlooks Indian Tree Golf Course. This wonderful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is situated on a spacious 1.6 acre lot with spectacular views of the entire front range. Features include: updated kitchen, giant family room, separate office, huge covered patio, spacious back yard with garden area, RV parking, no HOA, spectacular sunsets and more! Additional .6 acre rear lot with separate access from 76th and Vance Drive is also available. Buy one or both. Hurry to see this for yourself!
